        see:the cut recurses — a grandchild cell solves inside a child that solved inside the root and every level is the same one engine
        see:the children tile their parent exactly at every level of the nest — the areas sum with no gap and no overlap down to the grandchildren
        see:a heavier seed claims more room — the power wall stands off proportional to weight so importance can drive area
        see:areas nest monotonically — each cell holds strictly less room than the scope it lives in
